JOHANNESBURG - Unicef has confirmed that the decomposed body found on Table Mountain this week is that of its missing employee Charlotte Nikoi.RIP Charlotte Nikoi, UNICEF executive, who was missing for 10 weeks and whose body was found on Tuesday on Table Mountain, Cape Town pic.twitter.com/Gr7rNOCrqqThe Ghanaian Nikoi had come to Cape Town on holiday with her family.They reported her missing after she failed to return from a hike on the mountain on 21 March.Nikoi was the associate director of human resources for the UN children's agency and based in New York.eNCA